Remote Fittings are fast, easy, and accurate, and they can be done from the comfort and privacy of your home or office.

Once you submit your Remote Fitting video, our team of certified fitting professionals will use our video fitting software to analyze your stroke and calculate your ideal length and lie angle. Then theyll send you an email confirming your specifications.

REMOTE FITTING

Tailor your game by optimizing your club length, lie angle, and other key fitting elements that impact accuracy, consistency, and comfort in your swing

3 Simple steps: Record a quick video, take a measurement, and submit the form below.

Totally free
89% of golfers see an improvement
As accurate as in person fitting
Submit before or after purchase

Record a video

Your video should be about 5 seconds in length and no larger than 5MB in file size.

  • Use a putter with a comfortable length. Don't worry about how it soles.
  • Have the camera level with the player's hands (roughly knee/thigh height.)
  • Find a level surface with a vertical wall edge or door jam in the background.
  • Line up the tip of your putter shaft with the edge of the wall or door jam.
  • Please make sure to wear golf or tennis shoes when shooting the video.

Technology that sets us apart

  • Advanced Video Fitting Software for Precision

    Utilizing cutting-edge video fitting technology, our team analyzes your swing with incredible precision. This advanced software captures key data points, from club path to impact angle, ensuring that every fitting recommendation is customized to your unique mechanics.

  • Real-Time Data Integration

    Our technology seamlessly integrates real-time data from your fitting video with performance metrics, helping us make on-the-spot adjustments and offering immediate feedback. Youll know exactly how your clubs should be fitted for optimal performance

  • Custom Club Specifications with Expert Insights

    No more one-size-fits-all guessing: experience the game-changing benefits of a putter built precisely for you.

What our customers say

  • Follow the directions on the video and its that easy. I got my results back in a few days and then had some emails back and forth with the fitter. I then ordered a Link.1 and sold my Scotty once it arrived. The fitter actually caught something I was doing that I did not realize (leaning WAY over my Scotty) and fit me into a more vertical lie angle. Overall I could not be happier.

    - Greg g.

  • Extremely happy with my LAB. One thing for me, I only had standard- length putters available to use in the video, but I always gripped down had a pretty strong idea I wanted something shorter. I didnt mention this but the fitter asked me if it was my preference to grip down or if I wanted to go shorter.

    - Greg g.

  • Sam Haan, CEO of LAB, says they use remote fitting for most of the tour players. If its good enough for them, its good enough for hackers like us.
